The <b>IDIAP Research Institute</b> is a semi-private non-profit research institute affiliated with the <link>
Swiss Federal Institute of Technology at Lausanne</link> (EPFL), and with the <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../348/342348.xml">
University of Geneva</link></university>
. The institute is located in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../062/657062.xml">
Martigny</link> in the <canton wordnetid="108540770" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../789/198789.xml">
Canton of Valais</link></canton>
, <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../748/26748.xml">
Switzerland</link></country>
.<p>

IDIAP carries out research in the areas of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../448/28448.xml">
Speech processing</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../596/6596.xml">
Computer vision</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../271/15271.xml">
Information retrieval</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../622/290622.xml">
Biometric authentication</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../243/2081243.xml">
Multimodal Interaction</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../488/233488.xml">
Machine learning</link>.</p>
<p>

